(2070, 133, 'faqs_0_question', 'How Long Does it Take to Have a Treatment?'),
(2071, 133, '_faqs_0_question', 'field_54577d39361ec'),
(2072, 133, 'faqs_0_answer', 'You will need to allow 1.5 hours for your first procedure. If you intend to have a “full face” (3 procedures together) then you should allow 3 hours in total.'),
(2073, 133, '_faqs_0_answer', 'field_54577d71361ed'),
(2074, 133, 'faqs_1_question', 'How Long Does it Last?'),
(2075, 133, '_faqs_1_question', 'field_54577d39361ec'),
(2076, 133, 'faqs_1_answer', 'Semi-Permanent Make-up should last for several years. Over that time the colour will fade and break down. It is suggested that you come back for a top up” procedure every 18 months/2 years to keep the look complete and fresh. A “top up” appointment is half the current full treatment price.'),
(2077, 133, '_faqs_1_answer', 'field_54577d71361ed'),
(2078, 133, 'faqs_2_question', 'Does It Hurt?'),
(2079, 133, '_faqs_2_question', 'field_54577d39361ec'),
(2080, 133, 'faqs_2_answer', 'Some clients feel no discomfort at all – others feel minimal discomfort. Topical anaesthetics are used to control pain tolerance. Clients say that having a procedure is similar to having their eyebrows plucked. Once the procedure is complete there is no discomfort whatsoever.'),
(2081, 133, '_faqs_2_answer', 'field_54577d71361ed'),
(2082, 133, 'faqs_3_question', 'What About After Care?'),
(2083, 133, '_faqs_3_question', 'field_54577d39361ec'),
(2084, 133, 'faqs_3_answer', 'You will be given a comprehensive after care guide after the treatment, along with verbal instructions.'),
(2085, 133, '_faqs_3_answer', 'field_54577d71361ed'),
(2086, 133, 'faqs_4_question', 'Is it Expensive?'),
(2087, 133, '_faqs_4_question', 'field_54577d39361ec'),
(2088, 133, 'faqs_4_answer', 'It is very little compared with the years that this will last you and it doesn’t run, smudge, or wash off. The cost of the procedure should not be the most important factor when choosing a permanent make-up technician but the quality of work, attention to detail and the technician’s skill in artistry and creating symmetry.'),
(2089, 133, '_faqs_4_answer', 'field_54577d71361ed'),
